{This is another example of "She who knows, goes."

WEST has a solid 18 points, (1 extra for the fifth Club), so when EAST opens 1NT 
she KNOWS that together they must hold at least 33 points. The may even have 35 points. 

In any case they should be in slam, so WEST GOES to 6NT.}

